 future, reigning tyrannical supercomputers teleport a cyborg assassin known as the \"Terminator\" back to 1984 to kill Sarah Connor, whose unborn son is destined to lead insurgents against 21st century mechanical hegemony. Meanwhile, the human-resistance movement dispatches a lone warrior to safeguard Sarah. Can he stop the virtually indestructible killing machine?","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"popularity":19.2865,"vote_count":14302,"poster_path":"/qvktm0BHcnmDpul4Hz01GIazWPr.jpg","release_date":"1984-10-26","vote_average":7.675,"backdrop_path":"/ffdqHMWkh1h9MABwIfbfRJhgFW6.jpg","original_title":"The Terminator","original_language":"en"},{"id":311,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time in America","video":false,"overview":"A former Prohibition-era Jewish gangster returns to the Lower East Side of Manhattan over thirty years later, where he once again must confront the ghosts and regrets of his old life.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":10.1914,"vote_count":5904,"poster_path":"/i0enkzsL5dPeneWnjl1fCWm6L7k.jpg","release_date":"1984-05-23","vote_average":8.386,"backdrop_path":"/xlDUjb0Q5Dv6jPQRF5VE4IMjIy.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time in America","original_language":"en"},{"id":246,"adult":false,"title":"Zatoichi","video":false,"overview":"Blind traveler Zatoichi is a master swordsman and a masseur with a fondness for gambling on dice games. When he arrives in a village torn apart by warring gangs, he sets out to protect the townspeople.","genre_ids":[12,18,28],"popularity":1.4277,"vote_count":932,"poster_path":"/iCIycswWbX1EDS6PYYBcR9ohrC.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-06","vote_average":7.237,"backdrop_path":"/kP6WiYHQUUXo6ZaXI06enkMsxkF.jpg","original_title":"座頭市","original_language":"ja"},{"id":296,"adult":false,"title":"Terminator 3: Rise of the Machines","video":false,"overview":"It's been 10 years since John Connor saved Earth from Judgment Day, and he's now living under the radar, steering clear of using anything Skynet can trace. That is, until he encounters T-X, a robotic assassin ordered to finish what T-1000 started. Good thing Connor's former nemesis, the Terminator, is back to aid the now-adult Connor … just like he promised.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"popularity":7.326,"vote_count":7112,"poster_path":"/vvevzdYIrk2636maNW4qeWmlPFG.jpg","release_date":"2003-07-02","vote_average":6.184,"backdrop_path":"/voVkSwgFYv9GOpRNfUAwj6qYRTL.jpg","original_title":"Terminator 3: Rise of the Machines","original_language":"en"},{"id":280,"adult":false,"title":"Terminator 2: Judgment Day","video":false,"overview":"Ten years after the events of the original, a reprogrammed T-800 is sent back in time to protect young John Connor from the shape-shifting T-1000. Together with his mother Sarah, he fights to stop Skynet from triggering a nuclear apocalypse.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"popularity":14.2933,"vote_count":13964,"poster_path":"/jFTVD4XoWQTcg7wdyJKa8PEds5q.jpg","release_date":"1991-07-03","vote_average":8.1,"backdrop_path":"/xKb6mtdfI5Qsggc44Hr9CCUDvaj.jpg","original_title":"Terminator 2: Judgment Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":1948,"adult":false,"title":"Crank","video":false,"overview":"Chev Chelios, a hit man wanting to go straight, lets his latest target slip away. Then he awakes the next morning to a phone call that informs him he has been poisoned and has only an hour to live unless he keeps adrenaline coursing through his body while he searches for an antidote.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":6.0772,"vote_count":4110,"poster_path":"/bbGOV9lES80el46Hj4GLj5zY25F.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-31","vote_average":6.652,"backdrop_path":"/8JPz1636hMcaADngF4H4KOxXfp1.jpg","original_title":"Crank","original_language":"en"},{"id":1966,"adult":false,"title":"Alexander","video":false,"overview":"Alexander, the King of Macedonia, leads his legions against the giant Persian Empire. After defeating the Persians, he leads his army across the then known world, venturing farther than any westerner had ever gone, all the way to 